          <msContents>
            <summary/>
            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
              <locus from="2ra" to="16vb"/>
              <locus from="19ra" to="24va"/>
              <note>The folios of the manuscript are misplaced, being rearranged wrongly together:
                the text is in disorder.</note>
              <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1450GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Krǝstos</title>
              <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
              <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                <locus target="#2ra"/> በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ፨ ንቀድም፡ እንከ፡ በረድኤተ፡
                እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ንጽሕፍ፡ ዜናሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ብእሴ፡ እግዚኣብሔር፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1661Alexis">ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ</persName>። ወልደ፡ቴዎዶስዮስ፡ንጉሥ፡ ዘ<placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2196Consta">ቈስጠንጥንያ</placeName>፨፨ </incipit>
            </msItem>
            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
              <locus from="17ra" to="18vb"/>
              <locus from="25ra" to="25vb"/>
              <locus from="28ra" to="38va"/>
              <note>Number of Miracles 8. The folios are misplaced, the text is in disorder. The
                right order of the miracles is: <locus from="28ra" to="35vb"/>, <locus from="36ra" to="36vb"/>, <locus from="17ra" to="18vb"/>, <locus from="37ra" to="37vb"/>,
                  <locus from="25ra" to="25vb"/>, <locus from="38ra" to="38va"/>. Folios missing
                between <locus target="#35"/> and <locus target="#36"/>, with consequent missing
                part of the text.</note>
              <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2384Taamme">Taʾammǝra Māryām</title>
              <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
              <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                <locus target="#28ra"/> በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ። ንቀድም፡ እንከ፡ በረድኤተ፡
                እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፨ ወእምዝ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ </incipit>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                <locus from="28rb" to="30ra"/>
                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3640Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of a rich man who cast a loaf to a
          beggar and was saved by the Virgin after being condemned by Jesus</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#28rb"/> ወሀሎ፡ እንከ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ባዕል፡ ፈድፋድ፡ ወይገብር፡ ተዝካራ፡
                  ለማርያም፡ ወይቄርብ፡ ቍርባነ፡ በበ፡ በዓላ፡ ለማርያም፡ </incipit>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                <locus from="30ra" to="33va"/>
                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3615Miracle">Miracle of Mary: The Story of the Cannibal of Qǝmr</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#30ra"/> ካልዕ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ጸሎታ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን። ወሀሎ፡ አ<pb n="30r"/>
                  <cb n="b"/>ሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡ በሃገረ፡ <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC5209Qemer">ቅምር፡</placeName> ክቡር፡ ዘመድ፡
                  በስምስ፡ ክርስትያናዊ፡ </incipit>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
                <locus from="33vb" to="35ra"/>
                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3596Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the youth Zechariah, from
          Rome</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#33vb"/> ሣልስ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ጸሎታ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን። ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ ብእሲ፡
                  በውእቱ፡ ሃገር፡ ወሀለወት፡ ውስተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ሃገር፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ </incipit>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4">
                <locus from="35ra" to="35vb"/>
                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3917Miracle">Miracle of Mary: How the Virgin Mary obtained forgiveness for
          a monk who mutilated himself after he had defiled himself</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <note>Folios missing after <locus target="#35v"/>: explicit missing.</note>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#35ra"/> ራብዕ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ የሀበነ፡ በረከታ፡ <pb n="35r"/>
                  <cb n="b"/>ወሀሎ፡ አሐዱ፡ መነኮስ፡ ዘይፈርሆ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዘይበኪ፡ መዓልተ፡ ወሌሊተ፡ ላዕለ፡ </incipit>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5">
                <locus from="36ra" to="36va"/>
                <title type="incomplete"/>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <note>Folios missing before <locus target="#36r"/>: incipit missing.</note>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.6">
                <locus from="36va" to="36vb"/>
                <locus from="17ra" to="18rb"/>
                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3692Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of a hanged brigand resuscitated
          because he loved the Virgin</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#36va"/> ሳድስ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ የሃሉ ምስ<add place="inline">ለገብራ፡ ሀብተ፡ ሥላሴ</add>ን። ወኮነት፡ እንከ፡ ብእሲት፡ መበለት፡ ነዳይት፡ ወባ<pb n="36r"/>
                  <cb n="b"/>ቲ፡ አሐደ፡ ወልደ፡ ወኮነት፡ ይእቲ፡ ብእሲት፡ </incipit>
                <note>The phrase ለገብራ፡ ሀብተ፡ ሥላሴ, with the personal name ሀብተ፡ ሥላሴ, has been added and
                  written (most probably by a more recent hand) over the original name mentioned in
                  the suplication formula, which is thus not legible anymore.<note/>
                </note>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7">
                <locus from="18rb" to="18vb"/>
                <locus from="37ra" to="37vb"/>
                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3612Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the Phoenician evil man called
          Bārok</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#18rb"/> ሳብእ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለማርያም፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ይምሔር፡(sic) ይምሀረነ፡<pb n="18v"/>
                  <cb n="a"/> በጸሎታ፡ አሜን። ወኮነ፡ ብእሲ፡ ድያቆን፡ ይፈቅድ፡ ይትአመን፡ በእንተ፡ ኃጣውኢሁ፡ ወእከይ፡ </incipit>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8">
                <locus from="25ra" to="25vb"/>
                <locus from="38ra" to="38va"/>
                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4048Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the virgin whom a magistrate
          wanted to corrupt</title>
                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  <locus target="#25ra"/> ሣምን፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ይምሐረነ፡ በጸሎታ፡ አሜን። ወሀሎ፡
                  ብእሲ፡ ውስተ፡ ሃገር፡ እምሠራዊተ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ክበር፡ በሀቤኁ። ወኮነ፡ ጽልሕወ፡ </incipit>
              </msItem>
            </msItem>
          </msContents>
