                  front and back side, as protective leaves of the text block; recent textile inlays
                  and sewing used as reinforcements of the quires; original boards and covers
                  missing.</decoNote>
                <decoNote xml:id="b2" type="bindingMaterial">
                  <material key="cardboard"/>
